(30, 'tom-cruise.jpg', 'Whatâ€™s so difficult with Tom Cruise? Itâ€™s pretty obvious. He seems to be a wee bit nuts. And mind you, itâ€™s not just hearsay because it has been well documented over and over again. From his condescension to reporters who ask personal questions, the couch jumping, the creepy and somewhat forced relationships, the self-seriousness, all signs pointing to a little crazy. The only compensation here is that heâ€™s good with his craft.', 'ten-actors-everyone-hates-to-work-with', 'Tom Cruise', 10, '111d827749092cb9a3ab55928193c0f8'),
