(34, 'christian-bale.jpg', 'Hereâ€™s another guy who seems to be a regular in this kind of lists. Bale is famous for clashing with producers and directors. Thereâ€™s even a leaked tape that showed him screaming at co-workers on Termination Salvation set.', 'ten-actors-everyone-hates-to-work-with', 'Christian Bale', 6, '7aac60c8c58389c0752123ef9d963cd4'),
(35, 'dustin-hoffman.jpg', 'What makes Hoffman worse than those who donâ€™t know that theyâ€™re difficult? Itâ€™s because he admits it himself that being difficult is part of his personality. He also claims that his dedication to the craft is the reason for his attitude issues. Is it a good excuse? You judge.', 'ten-actors-everyone-hates-to-work-with', 'Dustin Hoffman', 5, '863158fd9114350cef94e00f9b284bf6'),
