(37, 'charlie-sheen.jpg', 'Oh, hereâ€™s Charlie Sheen. Who doesnâ€™t know about his all too public displays of sheer narcissism? And if this is not enough, you might also want to add in that his drug addiction that he has no plans of kicking is what made him lose his Two and a Half Men spot.', 'ten-actors-everyone-hates-to-work-with', 'Charlie Sheen', 3, '6d85c14fd9031cdb6d4b3bab4eb99889'),
