(46, 'snapchat-no-screenshot.jpg', 'This one has some hassle, but itâ€™s simple. Turn your phone on airplane mode, take your screenshot and then log out of the app. Afterwards, turn off airplane mode and then log back in.', '9-snapchat-hacks-tricks', 'Screenshot Secretly', 3, '72f36d124079c94670e2886290acca7f'),
