(48, 'snapchat-unlimited-text.jpg', 'This oneâ€™s simple. Tap on your screen to write some text. After youâ€™ve reached the limit, fear not, just record the rest of your caption with the dictation feature on both iPhones and Androids. Once youâ€™re finished, click the â€œTâ€ icon.', '9-snapchat-hacks-tricks', 'Unlimited Text', 1, 'e52bc43c4352b041810d2c7d2e53544d'),
(49, '3d-printed-camera.jpg', 'With the use of a 3D printer, you can now print a camera. The cameraâ€™s picture is not that great, but it does equate to something! It also does for an awesome gift; I mean who doesnâ€™t want a camera thatâ€™s 3D printed out of scratch?', 'ten-crazy-3d-printed-things', 'Camera', 10, 'd15c131ed908e4f5d6c1c4e90bb2571d'),
(50, '3d-printed-guitar.jpg', 'Want to learn a musical instrument? Just 3D print your instrument of choice and begin playing. Seriously! The 3D printer can print out anything from a violin to a guitar. Just wait while it processes and voila! Psst, if you want to be a pro, then you shouldnâ€™t 3D print any musical instrument because the sound quality is kind of bad.', 'ten-crazy-3d-printed-things', 'Musical Instruments', 9, '031f4cdd718e95c9e495281883b88f5f'),
(51, '3d-printed-birdhouse.jpg', 'Almost every person loves birds. With the 3D printer, you can build little houses for the small animals. Whatâ€™s even cooler? The houses are fully customizable. You can design and play around with the color, shape, and look of the bird house! You donâ€™t even have to do it yourself, the printer does it for you!', 'ten-crazy-3d-printed-things', 'Intricate Birdhouses', 8, 'ea0030fa5da1bea101f397a79fa211a8'),
(52, '3d-printed-obama-bust.jpg', 'You can print perfect figurines and busts of yourself, your loved ones, or your family. Have a narcissistic friend? Make one of him/her and give it to them as a gift!', 'ten-crazy-3d-printed-things', 'Custom Figurines', 7, '01fbbe12ba1463cee655d86ba57eb92b'),
(53, '3d-printed-gun.jpg', 'Weapon lovers can make 3D printed guns with the printer. An American based company made a high tech gun with only 16 plastic parts, and it actually works! Some are very skeptical about this idea, but this article will only advocate how far we have come in technology!', 'ten-crazy-3d-printed-things', 'Guns', 6, '42785a4141751620a6177e8bc745adec'),
(54, '3d-printed-arm.jpg', 'Arms, ears, noses, and more can all be 3D printed and used. In the medical world, the future of 3D printed body parts is very bright, but research right now is still at the beginning stage.', 'ten-crazy-3d-printed-things', 'Body Parts', 5, 'c192e727c59f80ed5ce86d381b122a1d'),
