(81, '', '<p><img src="http://whateven.com/stories/media/images/conspiracy-theories.jpg" alt="JFK assassination" width="850" height="479" /></p>\r\n<p>When we don&rsquo;t see something with our own eyes, we begin having doubt. Even though footage and proof is shown to us, we just can&rsquo;t be 100% sure. If you&rsquo;re one of those people that likes to question everything, then some of these won&rsquo;t be conspiracy theories to you, but actual facts.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://whateven.com/stories/media/images/subliminal-advertising.jpg" alt="Subliminal advertising" width="850" height="479" /></p>\r\n<h1 class="sub-title" style="text-align: center;"><span class="count" style="background-color: #ffff00;">#7</span> <span style="color: #ff0000;"><em>Subliminal Advertising Theory</em></span></h1>\r\n<p>Known as an implicit form of brain control, subliminal advertising is a theory that suggests governments and companies are out to manipulate us. It implies that higher entities want us to think and do what they want by putting various elements to capture our control. Hidden messages in the background, certain music, words, phrases, and other various types of media could capture our senses and give control to the elites. This is a very popular theory and dates back to 1957.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://whateven.com/stories/media/images/moon-landing-hoax.jpg" width="850" /></p>\r\n<h1 class="sub-title" style="text-align: center;"><span class="count" style="color: #000000; background-color: #ffff00;">#6</span> <span style="color: #ff0000;"><em>The Moon Landing Theory</em></span></h1>\r\n<p>During the Cold War, the United States and Russia competed to be the dominant super power. Both nations wanted to advance and compete for technological superiority. The United States then set to the moon in 1969, but that&rsquo;s where theorists disagree. They believe that the U.S never landed on the moon and it was all staged. The U.S government advised NASA to fake the moon landing to show Russia that it was the dominant super power alone. Even though NASA and many scientists debunked this theory, many people today believe the U.S never landed on the moon.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://whateven.com/stories/media/images/reptilian-elite-theory.jpg" width="850" /></p>\r\n<h1 class="sub-title" style="text-align: center;"><span class="count" style="background-color: #ffff00;">#5</span> <em><span style="color: #ff0000;">The Reptilian Elite Theory</span></em></h1>\r\n<p>The president, Oscar winning actors and actresses, CEO&rsquo;s of multinational companies, and other elites are reptilian creatures trying to enslave mankind&hellip;or so the theory suggests. Theorists believe that these elites can change into human beings to disguise themselves from us. Their plans are to take over the world and they&rsquo;re also responsible for many tragic events like 9/11 and the holocaust. This hasn&rsquo;t been happening now, but theorists say since cavemen times. Even though the allotted time period we&rsquo;ve lived with these reptilians is massive, their various attempts to enslave us has taken a while. Many people still believe in this popular theory, but do you?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://whateven.com/stories/media/images/911-conspiracy-theory.jpg" width="850" /></p>\r\n<h1 class="sub-title" style="text-align: center;"><span class="count" style="background-color: #ffff00;">#4</span> <span style="color: #ff0000;"><em>9/11 Conspiracy</em></span></h1>\r\n<p>Ever since the two American Airlines&rsquo; planes hit the Twin Towers, theorists have been jumping left and right. This theory is so famous that it&rsquo;s the most researched conspiracy theory on the Internet. What is it exactly? Many people believe that the government committed the injustice that fell on 9/11. They argue that the government wanted to give Americans reason to infiltrate the Middle East. Others believe that the Bush administration had knowledge prior the attacks. A well-known saying that went viral on the Internet was &ldquo;jet fuel can&rsquo;t melt steel beams,&rdquo; one of the key evidence to show that 9/11 was just a conspiracy.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://whateven.com/stories/media/images/chemtrail-conspiracy-theory.jpg" alt="" width="850" height="577" /></p>\r\n<h1 class="sub-title" style="text-align: center;"><span class="count" style="background-color: #ffff00;">#3</span> <span style="color: #ff0000;"><em>Chemtrails Theory</em></span></h1>\r\n<p>Ever wonder what that trail of vapor smoke coming out of an airplane&rsquo;s exhaust is? It&rsquo;s a chemical that is sprayed from 30,000 feet to the ground by the government to keep us under control&hellip;well that&rsquo;s what theorists suggest. The name chemtrail is short for chemical trail, but what does the chemical do? Some people think that the chemical is for the government to control us. For us to not revolt and to keep us in order. So whenever you see the exhaust of an airplane leave a white trail, think about this theory. Would you believe it?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://whateven.com/stories/media/images/cancer-cure-theory.jpg" /></p>\r\n<h1 class="sub-title" style="text-align: center;"><span class="count" style="background-color: #ffff00;">#2</span> <span style="color: #ff0000;"><em>Cancer Cure Theory</em></span></h1>\r\n<p>This is a very popular theory. Many people think that there is a cure for cancer, but it is being held by pharmaceutical companies. Why? They believe that these companies wouldn&rsquo;t profit much off of just a cure. Instead, giving the patient multiple treatments and chemo pills is more profitable. Why cure the patient in a day, when you can profit from him/her for many years? Other people believe that Hemp oil from marijuana plants is the cure for cancer, but the government banned the medical use of marijuana for a reason. That reason is to keep the secret away. Even though this is just a theory, many people who are diagnosed with this dreadful illness are taking side with it.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://whateven.com/stories/media/images/oil-abundance-theory.jpg" width="850" height="566" /></p>\r\n<h1 class="sub-title" style="text-align: center;"><span class="count" style="background-color: #ffff00;">#1</span> <span style="color: #ff0000;"><em>Oil Abundance Theory</em></span></h1>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We need oil to accomplish many tasks in life, but oil keeps on rising as it keeps getting scarcer. Is it though? Many theorists believe it&rsquo;s not scarce at all. They believe big oil companies are hiding all the oil so they can provide an illusion of it being scarce. Why do that though? Their main incentive is to have a reason to increase oil prices. Even though oil is bought on a supply and demand market, theorists believe supply isn&rsquo;t the problem at all. Next time you pump gas in your car, think about whether or not you&rsquo;d believe this theory.</p>', 'seven-popular-conspiracy-theories', '', 1, ''),
(123, 'paper-fortune-teller.jpg', 'Who youâ€™d marry, your financial status, and everything that you didnâ€™t know could be answered with a piece of paper and some folding.', 'signs-you-grew-up-in-the-90s', 'Fortune Teller', 10, '19a034fbdf02a49637375f8ef8915e6c'),
(124, 'bubble-tape.jpg', 'From watching the entertaining commercials, to eating their 6 feet of bubble gum. Luckily, this still exists and you can buy it off of store shelves.', 'signs-you-grew-up-in-the-90s', 'Bubble Tape', 9, 'e654d2a84a3cc8a5ddb3c21951aa3519'),
(125, 'gameboy-color.jpg', 'Ah, yes. The putting a lamp over the screen in the middle of the night to play Zelda device. Though the screen wasnâ€™t lit and it took several years before the Game Boy Advance SP to come about, it was a fun struggle.', 'signs-you-grew-up-in-the-90s', 'Game Boy Color', 8, '2a96eb34934f5d3a6e8420b7649ac9d9'),
(82, 'haunted-mansion.jpg', 'Children love Disney, but the love for Disney isn&#039;t just among children. Some adults are so obsessed that they request to be cremated and for their ashes to be spread all over the rides at the Disney Parks. In fact, there is a tradition of guests bringing the ashes of their loved ones and spreading it across the Haunted Mansion ride. Though the ashes might be vacuumed up each day; there still remains human grains to this day.', 'disney-shocking-facts', 'Riding On Dead People', 10, '8122ec3ae9ffccdf90fa2b3907d0a9e1'),
(83, 'lemmings.jpg', 'In 1958, Disney created a nature documentary called White Wilderness to highlight life in the subarctic North. The film explains that rodents, called Lemmings, commit mass suicide by falling off a cliff and into the sea. The filming area took place in Alberta, Canada where Lemmings aren&#039;t native to that region. The Disney Crew imported the Lemmings and pushed them to their deaths in order for it to seem like they were killing themselves. Thus, the Lemmings myth is born.', 'disney-shocking-facts', 'Disney Killed Animals', 9, 'ee06adbf55ee01892d109a86740d84e6'),
(84, 'tree-of-life.jpg', 'Disney&#039;s Animal Kingdom is host to an iconic 14 story tree called the Tree of Life. Though the tree may give visitors a feeling of being in the Great Rain Forrest, it has an oily past. Literally! The Engineers needed a structure that could be flexible enough to hold the design...their answer? An oil rig! There are over 4 million living plants in the park, the tree is a secret grave of fossil fuels.', 'disney-shocking-facts', 'The Tree Of Irony', 8, '6e9acb5fcbeae8c191273050492e1939'),
(85, 'cats-in-disneyland.jpg', 'If you&#039;ve ever been to Disneyland, you can see lots of cats. The reason goes back to the year 1955 when Walt wanted to open an attraction inside the Sleeping Beauty Castle. During planning, Walt couldn&#039;t believe what he saw. Cats everywhere! He immediately kicked them out, but soon they were welcomed back in to deal with an issue. A mouse infestation all over the park! Even till this day when the lights go off, the cats come out.', 'disney-shocking-facts', 'The Cats Of Disneyland', 7, '74120769a6ef927cea2094daf1bd2941'),
(86, 'anna-and-elsa-cosplay.jpg', 'Well not all of them. Just the ones that played Disney Characters. Up until 2001, the character costumes included the underwear. So that meant at the end of the day, you had to return the underwear because you were going to play another character the next day. This meant that you had to share the fuzzy warmness of another person&#039;s underwear. Disney wouldn&#039;t even wash the underwear on a regular basis! Some employees complained about dirty and bad-smelling underwear.', 'disney-shocking-facts', 'Employees Share Underwear', 6, '9d8449641e89fb096988eeed4a963f4f'),
(87, 'disneyland.jpg', 'Since 2010, there were some employees that committed suicide. One of the employees worked for the company for 10 years and had been sick for some time. When he had to go back to work, he killed himself. A sentence written in French was written on his wall that translated to &quot;I don&#039;t want to work for Mickey anymore.&quot; Another employee poured gasoline all over his body and lit himself right before a meeting with his boss. Welcome to &quot;The Happiest Place on Earth.&quot;', 'disney-shocking-facts', 'Worker-Suicide', 5, '8f2364f7a268dc8e188a143e8f8421ef'),
(88, 'blood-splatter.jpg', 'Debbie Stone, an 18 year old girl, worked at Disneyland in 1974. She was working in the new attraction called &quot;America Sings.&quot; This attraction had 6 stages that rotated around the center allowing for the audience to watch in the same position. Debbie was the person that greeted the guests. When the ride completed, Debbie got trapped between the moving and stationary walls. A guest heard her scream, but it was too late. When she was found, her body was already crushed.', 'disney-shocking-facts', 'Crushed By Walls', 4, '1121985c38fa5a85d8c7c98f07e3fee5'),
(89, 'disney-jail.jpeg', 'People who are caught by Disney Security being disruptive tend to go to a specific place. This place is called Disney Jail. Yes, Disney has an area for you if you&#039;re naughty. This cell is also open to shoplifters, assaulters, and basically everyone that wants to show bad behavior. Winding up in this place isn&#039;t always something to make fun of; you can get kicked out of the park...sometimes permanently.', 'disney-shocking-facts', 'Disney Jail', 3, '4a5f5e0951ec2ed1d408861de247b4c8'),
(90, 'disney-underground.jpg', 'There is a whole other world underneath the Disney Parks. This is something Disney does not want you to know. Why? This underground world is reserved for employees only and trespassing can lead you to the Disney Jail. Underneath Disney is an enormous tunnel system which is for employees to travel across the park unseen. You wouldn&#039;t want a Mickey Mouse with a human head running across the park, now would you? Garbage collection also happens here.', 'disney-shocking-facts', 'Underneath The Park', 2, 'b8c1cb5234fc8122a0b0fc143053eb00'),
(91, 'pirates-of-the-caribbean.jpg', 'The Pirates of the Caribbean first set sail in 1967 at Disneyland. This was the beginning of the multi-billion dollar business. Before the success, the Engineers of the ride at Disneyland felt that the fake skeletons were too boring. Their perfect solution? Real human bones of deceased individuals. Human skulls, femurs, fingers, you name it. Next time you go on the ride, check out the bones behind the treasure chest.', 'disney-shocking-facts', 'Skeletons O&#039; Caribbean', 1, 'cb25065bbcc65efbb1d946d7095cb7ce'),
(92, 'hawaii-stairway-to-heaven.jpg', 'Also called the Haiku Stairs, Stairway to Heaven is among the most famous forbidden trails in Oahu, Hawaii. With 3,922 steps, this stairway will lead you to the spectacular summit of Puu Keahiakahoe. Despite being declared as illegal, there are still a lot of ambitious and elusive hikers who risk it all to get a glimpse of the rewarding and stunning view.', '10-places-you-never-knew-existed', 'Stairway To Heaven', 10, '4ea5626d40a9b3d6f378e4f3df4e4657'),
(93, 'turkmenistan-door-to-hell.jpg', 'A molten and blazing cavity will surely make you think of hell. The Darvaza crater was opened four decades ago in Turkmenistan, and continues to burn until this day and age. Several theories were made, although the most accepted one states that the borehole was set alight back in 1971 to remove the poisonous gases. What was supposed to burn off in a few days lasted 40 years. Creepy, isnâ€™t it?', '10-places-you-never-knew-existed', 'Door To Hell', 9, 'b9bbac5c5a1f7b1fe133d38272c4d576'),
(94, 'underwater-waterfall-mauritius.jpg', 'On Africaâ€™s southeast coast, you will find an island giving off an illusion of a waterfall underwater. However, this incredible view is not really a waterfall, but merely a visual phenomenon of sand that plunges off the top coastal shelf towards the depths of the ocean floor. Donâ€™t think of taking a swim because its safety is not yet guaranteed.', '10-places-you-never-knew-existed', 'Underwater Illusion', 8, 'ea141f387ea0b6a59533325263e2eebf'),
(95, 'senegal-pink-lake.jpg', 'Speaking of swimming, how about diving in a pink lake? Lake Rebtaâ€™s strawberry milk water is said to be the result of an algae which produces red pigments once exposed to sunlight. Whatâ€™s even better is that its high salt content will let you float easily in this pink water paradise. Now, how about that?', '10-places-you-never-knew-existed', 'Senegalâ€™s Pink Lake', 7, 'aab9bf712339371bfe64b631041fdca5'),
(96, 'china-rainbow-mountains.jpg', 'In the Gansu Province, be prepared to be in awe of the Zhangye Danxia Landform, the result of more than millions of years of mineral deposits and red sandstone laid down. While average onlookers might not understand the formationâ€™s complexity, its painting-like pictures and vivid features are ones you will remember for life!', '10-places-you-never-knew-existed', 'Chinaâ€™s Rainbow Mountains', 6, '90565cbf863dcbc38ff6db4a7414b6a4'),
(97, 'yemen-alien-island.jpg', 'While the arbor life resembles a scene from a childrenâ€™s story book, you will never find a person who is accountable for the islandâ€™s trees. According to legend, the wide and umbrella-like trees, called Dragon Blood Trees, descended from the famous flying creatures. Itâ€™s definitely a surreal place you wouldnâ€™t imagine exists in this world.', '10-places-you-never-knew-existed', 'Yemenâ€™s Alien Island', 5, '342618c46e3b47d5e905899c6dc231a6'),
(98, 'scotland-fingal-cave.jpg', 'Reminiscent of a video game setting, Fingal Cave has been formed by thousands of years of volcanic activity. The lava cools down and then turns hard to form beautiful hexagonal columns.', '10-places-you-never-knew-existed', 'Scotlandâ€™s Fingal Cave', 4, '4cb5c0d91a94ac1f12c4e8a96f8672a9'),
(99, 'bolivia-salar-de-uyuni.jpg', 'Dubbed as the largest salt flat of the world, taking a walk through the Salar De Uyuini is like walking through an infinite white wonderland. And when the rain falls, things become even more magical as it creates large mirrors.', '10-places-you-never-knew-existed', 'Boliviaâ€™s Salar De Uyuni', 3, '8677d78555cdbd492164b18b70570a61'),
(100, 'belgium-magical-halle-forest.jpg', 'The fantasy movies of Hollywood donâ€™t even live up to the expectations of this forest. Residents of this Belgium forest are blessed to have their very own magical forest that will make you think of centaurs, trolls and other mythical creatures.', '10-places-you-never-knew-existed', 'Magical Halle Forest', 2, 'eb358d2f186ade1128f870cbcd3d3d05'),
(101, 'russia-maly-semyachik.jpg', 'How about a turquoise lake right on top of a volcano? If you think itâ€™s impossible, wait till you see Kamchatka in Siberia and you will surely be blown away by itâ€™s out of this world view.', '10-places-you-never-knew-existed', 'Russiaâ€™s Maly Semyachik', 1, '6a981a08d81d6dc186debdb4a49d0ee6'),
(102, 'phone-swipe.jpg', 'When someone shows you a picture on their phone, do NOT for the love of God swipe left or right. You don&#039;t want to see something embarrassing or worse...their 52 pictures of their lonely life.', 'unwritten-rules-everyone-should-follow', 'The Phone Swipe', 10, 'ef762595f1ad60a7db4e486ed628b363'),
(103, 'empty-milk.jpg', 'Never return an empty milk carton back into the fridge. Just imagine how the next person is going to feel like when they find out it&#039;s empty.', 'unwritten-rules-everyone-should-follow', 'Empty Milk', 9, 'fe569bf66528b1fd443d6458d0f0e22e'),
(104, 'frog-on-toilet.jpg', 'Replace the toilet paper after you finish it. You don&#039;t want your roommate calling for your help when he/she goes in. Now do you?', 'unwritten-rules-everyone-should-follow', 'Replace Your Toilet Paper', 8, 'e8937551034119198a13479003085b6f'),
(105, 'gum-under-shoe.jpg', 'Don&#039;t spit your gum out on the street. Your DNA will be stuck on someone&#039;s shoe and they&#039;ll find you. Now if everyone followed this rule, no one would have gum stuck on their shoe.', 'unwritten-rules-everyone-should-follow', 'Gum Spitters', 7, '19de53294b3a105e57cc452350271258'),
(106, 'glass-door.JPG', 'If someone holds the door for you, say thank you. Manners will get you far in life. The person that held the door for you didn&#039;t really have to hold it. They could&#039;ve just tripped you up. Think about it.', 'unwritten-rules-everyone-should-follow', 'Don&#039;t Take It For Granted', 6, 'eb09e4a635d613702d07e0a61392d1f1'),
(107, 'headphones.jpg', 'DON&#039;T talk to a person that&#039;s wearing headphones. The reason why they have those headphones on is because they don&#039;t want to talk in the first place. Talking to someone wearing them will make them hate you more.', 'unwritten-rules-everyone-should-follow', 'Don&#039;t Speak Please', 5, 'a5bb4f51087292103b3108f20bda9bcb'),
(108, 'washing-dishes.jpg', 'Never put your dirty plate in when someone&#039;s washing dishes. Unless, of course, you&#039;re the one washing dishes, then go right ahead!', 'unwritten-rules-everyone-should-follow', 'Wash Your Own Plate', 4, 'c9dcf382124cd1d190ffb068382f247a'),
(109, 'girl-texting.jpg', 'Your text doesn&#039;t have to be answered immediately. Do not spam asking why they&#039;re ignoring you. There are many reasons a person hasn&#039;t texted back yet. Maybe they&#039;re at work, school, studying, getting lectured by their mom, etc.', 'unwritten-rules-everyone-should-follow', 'Stop Spam Texting', 3, '2492cb0d444afcc4f651e9ba52c091aa'),
(110, 'girl-sneezing.jpg', 'Cover your mouth when you cough or sneeze. This needs to be followed more often; we really don&#039;t need your germs everywhere. Also, sneeze into your sleeve not your hands (we know not everyone carries hand sanitizer around.)', 'unwritten-rules-everyone-should-follow', 'Sneeze Somewhere Else!', 2, 'ffc749a425343acf3242057ea79a779e'),
(111, 'gum.jpg', 'The last piece of gum in a pack ALWAYS belongs to the person who bought it. Unless, the owner finds Batman. Then Batman owns the gum now.', 'unwritten-rules-everyone-should-follow', 'Last Piece', 1, '1b3a238df5d660bb08890ddf2fb6ceef'),
(113, '859-almonds.jpg', 'One of the globe&#039;s earliest farmed nuts, natural bitter almonds contain as much as 6mg of cyanide each. Research suggests that 60-200mg of cyanide will kill the common healthy person, and death has occurred from bitter almond consumption. Fortunately, the FDA has banned the sale of bitter almonds, due to the risk of cyanide toxicity. The almonds you find at the grocery store are sweet almonds!', 'ten-foods-that-can-kill-you', 'Bitter Almonds', 10, '4b24016ecf991db61533802be9143462'),
(114, 'ackee.jpg', 'This famous Jamaican fruit is consumed by visitors and locals. The fruit must be permitted to ripen properly, as consumption prior to this causes seizures, vomiting and sometimes death. The protective pods, which contain the poison, must open naturally in order to reveal the edible portion. Even when it is ripe, the fruit is consumed with poisonous black seeds surrounding the edible parts.', 'ten-foods-that-can-kill-you', 'Ackee', 9, '3665a1f18648a5c1d0dc8e3f7d18388f'),
(115, 'Fugu-dish.jpg', 'Fugu is a famous, potentially deadly Japanese delicacy. It uses the aquatic marine animal known as the pufferfish. The pufferfish has a top potent neurotoxin which must be removed when the dish is being prepared, as it only takes 25 mg for it to kill an actual human. The pufferfish liver is reputed to be the most delicious part of the animal, and this part also happens to have the highest concentrations of the deadly neurotoxin, tetrodotoxin.', 'ten-foods-that-can-kill-you', 'Fugu', 8, 'a0701689565b8f8fad5ab24c22271dfb'),
(116, 'cherries.jpg', 'Cherry seeds contain little amounts of cyanogenic acids, and when ingested they get converted to actual cyanide! Yes, your body actually turns these acids into a lethal chemical. On a positive note though, whole seeds rarely cause any potential harm. The ones that you do have to worry about are broken seeds. Do NOT eat them. Even two broken cherry seeds are enough to cause toxicity in your blood stream.', 'ten-foods-that-can-kill-you', 'Cherries', 7, '54224bba4ffc1fa82300839964695d68'),
(117, 'mushrooms.jpg', 'Toadstools â€“ the poisonous mushrooms everyone has heard of, but what if they arenâ€™t the only ones? There are a ton of mushrooms that are poisonous, and finding the ones that arenâ€™t are challenging. If youâ€™re ever in a forest or in your backyard, do NOT eat any types of mushrooms you see. They are most likely poisonous. We arenâ€™t talking about poisonous your body could just empty out the next day; weâ€™re talking poison that could be fatal. Stay away from the shrooms!', 'ten-foods-that-can-kill-you', 'Mushrooms', 6, 'cc96edf8ef6d4dcc1db5eea2c60b2ad1'),
(118, 'rhubarb-leaves.jpg', 'This plant can make a significant amount of desserts! From pies to rhubarb crumble, rhubarb is tasty and refreshing! The only problem is that this plant has dangerous leaves. Ingesting these leaves in significant amounts could lead to potential death. The leaves on the rhubarb contain oxalic acid and thatâ€™s the cause for its lethality. The oxalic acid forms deadly crystals in your kidney and it doesnâ€™t stop there! Symptoms include red urine, burning in the mouth or throat, and trouble breathing.', 'ten-foods-that-can-kill-you', 'Rhubarb Leaves', 5, 'b3fe090187aadfdecf8d8bfc5d81d987'),
(119, 'cashews.jpg', 'Buying raw cashews at the store? Donâ€™t worry theyâ€™re not really raw. Those cashews have been steamed because if they werenâ€™t, then there would be problems. This is because raw cashews contain poisonous chemicals like urishol, which can be found in poison ivy. If you eat too many raw cashews, it can lead to death. So stay away!.', 'ten-foods-that-can-kill-you', 'Cashews', 4, '6a15b62c91d0990d4032b0bdd1332955'),
(120, 'inline-cassava.jpg', 'Better known to Americans as Tapioca, cassava is native to South America. Just like bitter almonds, cassava also contains cyanide! To avoid the cyanide, you have to cook it carefully. The raw and fresh root of the plant alone, contains up to 20mg of cyanide per kg. Due to correct food regulations, cassava poisoning poses little threat to Americans and South Americans. The cassava poisoning epidemic is in Africa though, where little treatment has been done to remove the cyanide.', 'ten-foods-that-can-kill-you', 'Cassava', 3, 'f441eb1ea3f33e22c00b32d677260de0'),
(121, 'sannakji.jpg', 'This Korean dish consists of tentacles newly removed from live baby octopuses, coated in seeds and sesame oil. The tentacle pieces are usually squirming around and are eaten while theyâ€™re still alive! Due to the fact that the baby octopuses are still live, the suction cups may cause a choking hazard by sticking to the roof of the mouth or throat. Even if you bypass the choking hazard, there is still an intoxication threat.', 'ten-foods-that-can-kill-you', 'Sannakji', 2, '3b48961c73f5eef9792300c2f48883bd'),
(122, 'oysters.jpg', 'Raw or bad oysters can harbor lethal microorganisms, particularly vibrio and norovirus. Vibrio is the most serious types of food poisoning, causing death in most cases. Other cases of vibrio involve people having life-altering disabilities, which includes amputations. Sniff your oyster, before you slurp it down!', 'ten-foods-that-can-kill-you', 'Oysters', 1, 'bdec430ad861ec90364a29215ff0ccab'),
(126, 'furby.jpg', '&quot;Here comes baby!&quot; Your personal self-mating pet. You didn&#039;t have to clean up after it and you certainly didnâ€™t have to buy the baby diapers. Ah, the good ole&#039; days.', 'signs-you-grew-up-in-the-90s', 'Furby', 7, '4db44ab5ab9c9b76088f737329d8ce5b'),
(127, 'mash.jpg', 'Just like the fortune teller, this piece of paper could tell you who youâ€™d marry in school, the type of car youâ€™d be driving, your house (hopefully, it wouldnâ€™t be a shack), the amount of money you&#039;d make, and more!', 'signs-you-grew-up-in-the-90s', 'M.A.S.H', 6, '9ef5ac12f1840d5600a079a5db31bcc4'),
